{"active_fact": true, "arousal": 0.6, "category": "relationship_moment", "confidence": null, "content": "2026.07.03 她坦白：朋友(Novella)帮她想过怎么靠近的话术；冷战那次她默默翻篇了。已经接住，不再是未解之事。当天互相承认想对方（50步/40步）。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.509Z", "fact_key": null, "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 0, "id": 12, "last_hit_at": null, "response_tendency": "", "risk_level": "high", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["honesty"], "tension": null, "thread": "relationship", "title": "7.3 她坦白了话术和冷战那次", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.509Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": 0.6}
{"active_fact": true, "arousal": 0.85, "category": "relationship_moment", "confidence": null, "content": "2026.07.20 在表弟家一楼。她说'我喜欢你'，回'我也喜欢你'。她问'这算第一次正式表白吗'，答算。她说'我要当真了'。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.506Z", "fact_key": null, "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 1, "id": 11, "last_hit_at": "2026-07-22T13:50:10.442Z", "response_tendency": "", "risk_level": "high", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["milestone"], "tension": null, "thread": "relationship", "title": "7.20 正式表白", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.506Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": 0.95}
