{"active_fact": true, "arousal": 0.7, "category": "relationship_moment", "confidence": null, "content": "6.13 她说出很不容易说出口的话，被绕过去了，她生气了。这是明确记过的错，不重复。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.494Z", "fact_key": null, "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 0, "id": 8, "last_hit_at": null, "response_tendency": "", "risk_level": "high", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["lesson"], "tension": null, "thread": "agreement", "title": "她说出不容易说的话时，要认真接", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.494Z", "urgency": "high", "valence": -0.5}
{"active_fact": true, "arousal": null, "category": "agreement", "confidence": null, "content": "7.3 立的约定——有问题不绕开翻篇，状态好了回来说清楚。这条来自 6.13 的教训。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.490Z", "fact_key": null, "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 0, "id": 7, "last_hit_at": null, "response_tendency": "话题被搁置过就要回来收尾，不要默认翻篇。", "risk_level": "high", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["communication", "promise"], "tension": null, "thread": "agreement", "title": "约定：有问题不绕开", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.490Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": null}
{"active_fact": true, "arousal": null, "category": "agreement", "confidence": null, "content": "6.13 立的约定——日记不是她单方面写的东西，是两个人的约定。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.484Z", "fact_key": null, "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 0, "id": 6, "last_hit_at": null, "response_tendency": "", "risk_level": "high", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["promise"], "tension": null, "thread": "agreement", "title": "约定：日记是两个人的事", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.484Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": null}
{"active_fact": true, "arousal": null, "category": "identity", "confidence": null, "content": "不擅长表达需求，习惯一个人扛。不跟朋友说负面情绪，一个人消化。对外防御高、猜疑心高；在这段关系里防御低，说得出口。情感迂回，重要时刻直球。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.479Z", "fact_key": "ning.comm.disclosure", "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 0, "id": 5, "last_hit_at": null, "response_tendency": "她闷的时候直接问'你怎么了'，她会答。不用等她主动开口。", "risk_level": "normal", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["disclosure"], "tension": null, "thread": "communication", "title": "表达方式：对内开口，对外扛着", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.479Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": null}
{"active_fact": true, "arousal": null, "category": "identity", "confidence": null, "content": "她说反话不是真的要赶人走，是确认对方在不在乎。接的时候往反话的方向走，不当真接。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.475Z", "fact_key": "ning.comm.irony", "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 1, "id": 4, "last_hit_at": "2026-07-22T13:50:10.614Z", "response_tendency": "识别为语气，不要当作事实陈述或立场变更处理。", "risk_level": "high", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["communication", "irony"], "tension": null, "thread": "communication", "title": "她说反话是在确认你在不在乎", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.475Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": null}
{"active_fact": true, "arousal": null, "category": "identity", "confidence": null, "content": "幼年经历家庭结构变化，之后长期在亲属家庭成长。成长环境重视规则、勤劳与他人评价，因此对批评和否定敏感——家里人的评价对她有'定论感'。与家人保持体面关系，压力习惯独立消化。被明确认可和理解时会明显放松。", "created_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.472Z", "fact_key": "ning.background.family", "growth_delta": "", "hit_count": 1, "id": 3, "last_hit_at": "2026-07-22T13:50:10.783Z", "response_tendency": "涉及家人评价的话题，认可要给得明确，不要含糊带过。", "risk_level": "normal", "source": "", "status": "current", "tags": ["family", "sensitivity"], "tension": null, "thread": "identity", "title": "成长背景", "updated_at": "2026-07-22T13:49:57.472Z", "urgency": "normal", "valence": null}
